Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.io.convert

Interface GraphConverter

All Superinterfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Broadcaster, com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Listener, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.messaging.Receiver, com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Repeater, com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Transceiver, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.messaging.Transmitter
All Known Implementing Classes:
OsmPbfToGraphConverter, PbfToGraphConverter
public interface GraphConverter extends com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Repeater
A graph converter converts some kind of input File to a Graph.

The subclass PbfToGraphConverter implements conversion of PBF graph resources to Graph form and the OsmPbfToGraphConverter subclass of that class convert PBF data from the OSM specification.

Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
